---
// src/components/FeedingScheme.astro
---
<section class="section-dark py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="gold-line mx-auto"></span>
      <h1 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white mb-4">
        Feeding Scheme – Winter 2025
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-amber-400 text-lg">NU1 &amp; NU2, Mdantsane</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
      <p>
        During the coldest months of 2025, eKoneni partnered with local families to prepare and deliver warm meals to over 120 children across NU1 and NU2. Many of these children would have gone to bed hungry without this support.
      </p>
      <p>
        What started as a simple idea quickly grew into something bigger. Families came together to cook, volunteers helped with delivery, and the community showed up in ways we didn’t expect. For many kids, these meals weren’t just food — they were warmth, care, and dignity.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Image/Video Placeholder -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="aspect-video bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-amber-400/10 flex items-center justify-center">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/1200x630/1f2937/9ca3af?text=Insert+Feeding+Scheme+Photos+&+Videos" 
             alt="Placeholder - Feeding Scheme" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3">Insert real photos and videos here</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400 text-black font-medium tracking-wide text-sm hover:bg-amber-300 transition-colors">
        Support this initiative →
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <a href="/community" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">← Back to Community Stories</a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>